Metorex Says Vale Isn’t Planning on Amending Its Takeover Bid for Company

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-07-11T07:07:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/metorex-says-vale-doesn-t-plan-on-amending-bid-for-south-african-company.html
Metorex Ltd. (MTX)  said it received
written notice from  Vale SA (VALE3)  that it doesn’t intend to amend its
offer for the South African company.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
